The paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for person re-identification, which is a computer vision problem. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves optimization and clustering, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper uses deep neural networks, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with security and privacy, which could make it relevant to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
